IMPORTANT TERMS:
machine learning
types:--supervised,unsupervised,reinforcement
APPLICATIONS:--
image recognition,speech recognition, prediction(traffic),
natural language processing, recommendation systems(product recommendation), self driving cars,filtering(email spam filtering), autonomous vehicles

recognition(pattern,image,face,speech)
filtering(email,malware)
prediction(traffic,)
recommendation
detection
translation
self driving
assistant

key concepts:
features,labels,datasets
training,testing sets
model,algorithms and parameters
Evaluation metrices:accuracy,precision,recall,F1 score.

Types of Machine learning:--
1.SUPERVISED LEARNING:--(classification,regression(linear,logistic),decision trees,random forests)
2.UNSUPERVISED LEARNING:--(Clustering(K-means,hierarchical,principal component analysis(PCA )),dimensionality reduction)
3.REINFOCEMENT LERNING:--(Agent,environment,rewards)
examples:Q-learning,deep reinforcement learning

DEEP LEARNING::--
ANN(artificial)
CNN (convulational)
RNN(recurrent)
LSTM(long-short term memory)

Basic concepts of scikit-learn

1.model fitting,predicting,cross-validation 2.supports supervised and unsupervised learning 3.provides various tools as --model fitting,model selection,model evaluation

